sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Vast Admin or Merchant
    participant FE as Admin / Merchant UI
    participant API as CashbackConfigurationController
    participant SVC as CashbackService
    participant REPO as CashbackConfigurationRepository
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant CACHE as Cache (Redis)

    U->>FE: Open Cashback settings
    FE->>API: GET /restaurants/{id}/cashback/config
    API->>SVC: getRestaurantConfig(id)
    SVC->>CACHE: get cashback_config:{id}
    alt cache hit
        CACHE-->>SVC: config
    else cache miss
        SVC->>REPO: getActiveByRestaurant(id)
        REPO->>DB: SELECT * FROM cashback_configurations WHERE restaurant_id=? ORDER BY version DESC LIMIT 1
        DB-->>REPO: latest version row
        REPO-->>SVC: config
        SVC->>CACHE: set cashback_config:{id} TTL=1h
    end
    SVC-->>API: config
    API-->>FE: 200 OK { config }
    FE-->>U: Show form (read-only fields if userType=restaurant && !merchant_can_edit)

    U->>FE: Submit changes (percentage, cap, expiration_days, ...)
    FE->>API: PUT /restaurants/{id}/cashback/config
    API->>SVC: setConfiguration(id, payload, updatedBy, userType)

    alt userType=restaurant
        SVC->>SVC: validate prohibited fields (is_active, is_mandatory_to_checkout, merchant_can_edit, vast_fee_percentage) absent
        SVC->>REPO: getLatestByRestaurant(id)
        REPO-->>SVC: latest
        SVC->>SVC: assert latest.merchant_can_edit == true
    end

    SVC->>SVC: validate ranges (1 <= percentage <= 100, cap_amount >= 0, expiration_days > 0, min_invoice_amount >= 0)
    SVC->>REPO: createNewVersion(payload, restaurantId, updatedBy)
    REPO->>DB: BEGIN
    REPO->>DB: SELECT MAX(version) FROM cashback_configurations WHERE restaurant_id=?
    DB-->>REPO: latest version v
    REPO->>DB: INSERT cashback_configurations (...payload..., version = v+1, updated_by, ...)
    DB-->>REPO: row inserted (id, version=v+1)
    REPO->>DB: COMMIT
    REPO-->>SVC: new config
    SVC->>CACHE: forget cashback_config:{id}
    SVC-->>API: new config
    API-->>FE: 200 OK { config }
    FE-->>U: Saved (history shows previous versions)

    Note over DB: Earlier versions remain immutable.<br/>Latest version is current.<br/>Lots reference configuration_version,<br/>so changes never alter earned terms.
